            <title>[SHDP-572] FsShell.chgrp fires a chmod operation on hadoop instead of chgrp</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SHDP-572</link>
                <project id="10801" key="SHDP">Spring for Apache Hadoop</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;org.springframework.data.hadoop.fs.FsShell shell;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
.&lt;br/&gt;
.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;shell.chgrp(true, &quot;group1&quot;, &quot;/path/to/hdfs/folder&quot;); &lt;/p&gt;

